> Hydrass left the base and  opned a comlink at Leo Prime "Ok kitty prime,
> send me the coordinates" then he send a enconded message at Inferno
> "Report."

There was a set of cordinates that quickly streamed through to HYDRAS,
filtered of course through the base communications net. Yes, the
systems that CYCLONUS, TARANTULUS and FRACTYL had put in place was
working well.

The co-ordinates matched an area just outside the communication black
out zone of the jungle along the same path that the others had taken
towards the jungle entrance - the one that followed the path the
dinosaurs had broken down when they stampeded out.

Although HYDRAS had called only for SKYSHADOW, VICE GRIP and DINOBOT,
CRYOTEK also transformed into beastmode and followed as well, his
great wings beating the air, seeming to glow with energy as the
absorbed the ambient thermal energies to power his systems.

He glanced back once to see if the spider was keeping up.

BLACKARACHNIA recieved a set of co-ordinates as well. "These are the
co-ordinates that Hydras recieved." TARANTULUS transmitted along thier
encrypted channel. "We need to know what is going on in there. If
Cryotek doesn't go, find a way to get there as well. That is our true
focus. Something is going on that we need to see."

Although there was no cackle from TARANTULUS, one could imagine him
rubbing his hands together throughtfully, his optics dark and
thoughtful, blazing out of the shadows of his quarters.

(TAG)

Preston
